- To install this module you need to install:
     + eBox components
        libebox
        ebox
        network
        firewall
	usersandgroups
	samba
     + Debian packages
        cupsys
	libnet-cups-perl
	foomatic-db
	foomatic-db-engine
	foomatic-filters
	foomatic-filters-ppds

- Once EBox base has been installed:
	
	./configure
	make install

  configure will autodetect EBox base path to install

- Update your sudoers file with the ebox-sudoers command.

- Do not run cupsys on startup, this module takes control of it:

mv /etc/rc2.d/SXXcupssys /etc/rc2.d/K20cupsys

- Stop cupsys if it's running.
